data.description: Welcome to our real estate listing for a charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home situated on a beautifully landscaped double lot in a convenient in-town location. This meticulously maintained property showcases a combination of stucco siding and stone veneer, along with vinyl windows, a durable metal roof, and an abundance of privacy. Let's delve into the captivating features of this remarkable home. As you approach the property, you'll immediately notice the impeccable landscaping that graces the double lot. The lush greenery, carefully manicured flower beds, and thoughtfully placed shrubs create a serene oasis that exudes tranquility. Whether you desire a peaceful retreat or an inviting space for outdoor entertaining, this property offers it all. Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an ideal layout for both daily living and hosting gatherings. Natural light floods the space, thanks to the strategically placed vinyl windows that not only offer energy efficiency but also enhance the overall aesthetics of the home. The kitchen is both functional and aesthetically pleasing, featuring modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or prefer simple meal preparation, this kitchen is sure to meet your needs. For your private showing, call Skye Coleman-Weisz at 307-851-0021 today!
